	                    <p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://blog.sabaitechnology.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/Open-vs-PPTP-1-01.png"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-4347" alt="Open vs PPTP 1-01" src="http://blog.sabaitechnology.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/Open-vs-PPTP-1-01.png" width="619" height="444" /></a></p>
